# Game Engine Rules

## Constraints

- **No UI imports** — Engine must not import React, Next.js, or DOM.
- **Pure logic** — Grid, Command Execution, Validator, Reward, State Machine are pure.
- **Testable** — Every public function must be unit-testable.

## Structure

- `packages/game-engine/src/` — Core engines
- `packages/game-engine/src/grid.ts` — Grid Engine
- `packages/game-engine/src/command.ts` — Command Execution Engine
- `packages/game-engine/src/validator.ts` — Puzzle Validator
- `packages/game-engine/src/reward.ts` — Reward Engine
- `packages/game-engine/src/state-machine.ts` — Level State Machine

## Contract

Engine exposes: `loadLevel(levelId)`, `executeAction(action)`, `getState()`. Never depends on UI.
